@startuml
title TuitionPayment Class Diagram - School Management System

hide circle

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ClassBorderColor #334155
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor white
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEF9C3
skinparam NoteBorderColor #A16207

class TuitionPayment {
  -id: bigint
  -student_id: bigint
  -parent_id: bigint
  -recorded_by: bigint
  -amount: integer
  -paid_on: date
  -method: string
  -reference: string
  -notes: string

  --
  +student(): BelongsTo
  +parent(): BelongsTo
  +recorder(): BelongsTo
}

note right of TuitionPayment
TuitionPayment stores payments made
for a student's course tuition.

It links each payment to the student,
optionally to the parent, and to the
user who recorded the payment.
end note

@enduml